      className=" flex justify-center items-center pb-[30px] "
      transitionName="slide-up"
    >
      <h2 class="section-title mb-2">About Us</h2>
    </AnimationCard>
    <div class="flex gap-6 max-tabletLand:flex-col">
      <AnimationCard className="pl-3" transitionName="slide-up">
        <p class="mb-4">
          We are Akeshya, a firm that specializes in web design and marketing.
          We help transform ideas into reality with a team of passionate graphic
          designers, web developers, and seasoned marketing advisors.
        </p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2.5">
          <li>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#14279b]">
              done_all
            </span> We started with a simple idea: do what is best for the client.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#14279b]">
              done_all
            </span> Our methodical and individual approach to each project delivers
            the finest possible results for your media.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#14279b]">
              done_all
            </span> Our day-to-day work is to solve your problems utilising the most
            up-to-date, practical adaptive technology, and we have a lot of fun doing
            it.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </AnimationCard>
      <AnimationCard transitionName="slide-up">
        <p class="mb-4">
          We're professional, but we're also friendly, and we'll always pay
          attention to your concerns. We expect to work with innovative people
